							<p>Canada, on the other hand, has become an IT hub and most of the tech and Pharma companies are looking at Toronto and Greater Toronto Area for expansion because of its abundant labor and infrastructure facilities. Due to the same time-zone and multiple immigration policies, Canada has become a preferred destination for Company Incorporation in North America. ASC’s Canada office is in Toronto and helps businesses from across the world to understand the market and establish their operations in Ontario, Quebec, Alberta, and British Columbia.  </p>
